Field Documentation

uint32_t pmhalTps65917RegulatorProp::ctrlRegAddr

The regulator control register address.

uint32_t pmhalTps65917RegulatorProp::forceRegAddr

The regulator force command voltage register address. Not all regulators have the force register; if not present the value of this field is expected to be NULL.

uint16_t pmhalTps65917RegulatorProp::maxVolt

Maximum voltage supported by the regulator in mV.

uint16_t pmhalTps65917RegulatorProp::slewRate

uint8_t pmhalTps65917RegulatorProp::stepVolt

Step voltage in mV.

uint8_t pmhalTps65917RegulatorProp::type

The regulator type namely PMHAL_TPS659039_SMPS or PMHAL_TPS659039_LDO.
